ndex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bdz1665702831587.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bdz1665702831587.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bdz1665702831587.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bdz1665702831587\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Define Tree Structure\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the hierarchical structure of items in the Tree widget.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__p_d9395e1_d9396e1_d9397e1\">Use <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span> to add or remove tree items from the tree.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__p_d9398e1_d9399e1_d9400e1\">Use the arrow buttons to move tree items in the tree structure.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__section_nkc_35k_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1089367e63\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__ul_mkr_35k_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4262e1_d4263e1_d4264e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eoz1665702831832.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eoz1665702831832.html\" title=\"Displays the icon used for the normal state of the selected tree item.\">Icon</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4265e1_d4266e1_d4267e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"khd1665702831945.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/khd1665702831945.html\" title=\"Displays the level of the selected tree item in the tree hierarchy.\">Level</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4268e1_d4269e1_d4270e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yog1665702832058.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yog1665702832058.html\" title=\"Specify the value used to identify the tree item.\">Identifier</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4271e1_d4272e1_d4273e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eea1665702832171.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eea1665702832171.html\" title=\"Enter the text displayed for the selected tree item at run time. This is the representation of the tree item's value.\">Item Text</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4274e1_d4275e1_d4276e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qvj1665702832292.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qvj1665702832292.html\" title=\"Select a type for the tree item.\">Tree Item Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4277e1_d4278e1_d4279e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vua1665702832405.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vua1665702832405.html\" title=\"Displays the role for the selected tree item as defined by the Type of tree item.\">Role</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__section_j51_j5k_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1089367e127\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__ul_iqt_n5k_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4280e1_d4281e1_d4282e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"moy1665702638031.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/moy1665702638031.html\" title=\"A tree widget is useful for displaying and maintaining hierarchical information.\">Defining Tree Widgets</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bdz1665702831587__li_d4283e1_d4284e1_d4285e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"okv1665702558483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/okv1665702558483.html\" title=\"The items listed in a tree widget typically represent a nested ValRep list. You can populate the initial list when defining the widget properties in the Component Editor. To make changes to the list, you must use ProcScript to update or rebuild the list.\">Defining and Updating ValRep Lists for the Tree Widget</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>utree (Tree)</a><p>The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419029\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419029\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Tree Structure Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Tree Structure Specify the hierarchical structure of items in the Tree widget. Use New and Delete to add or remove tree items from the tree. Use the arrow buttons to move tree items in the tree structure. Fields Icon Level Identifier Item Text Tree Item Type Role How to Defining Tree Widgets Defining and Updating ValRep Lists for the Tree Widget Related Links utree (Tree) The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}